## Before you change this repo

1. Read **`AGENTS.md`** at the repository root.
2. For every file you create or edit, read each **`.github/instructions/*.instructions.md`** whose YAML **`applyTo`** glob matches that path, and follow the markdown body.

Treat those sources as the project’s conventions (layering, tests, API shape, etc.). Prefer matching existing modules (`api/users`, `domains/wedding_sites`, `domains/users`, …) when unsure.
